---++ Action Items

   * Ruth (Executive Director) will approach ATLAS  (Torre and Michael) management and request help from the council as needed – regarding sharing.  Also audit the policies.  Joining – check.
   * Ruth will have a meeting about IRODS, with regard to CoralWMS.
   * Kent (Council Co-chair) will make sure the OSG’ proposal is consistent with the by-laws, and vice versa.  By-laws should reflect reality.  
   * Kent will come back with recommendations for changes to by-laws.
   * Kent will (a) poll council for dates (mid-May) and (b) schedule an ad hoc council face-to-face meeting.


